        :Cond_STV_Metric_OperationalState_Enabled ,             ## ST-V metric is being measured/calculated
         ## epistemic representation
        :Cond_STV_Metric_MagnitudeState_High                        ## ST-V_metric hasMagnitudeState = High (deviant value)  
