        ## PM: Check later - singular ST-segment deviations are not clinically interpretable in a uniform manner.
        :Cond_CardiacDepolarizationProperty_ObservationState_Monitored , ## CardiacDepolarizationProperty is being monitored (e.g. via ST-segment analysis)
        :Cond_CardiacDepolarizationProperty_MagnitudeState_High                     ## CardiacDepolarizationProperty hasMagnitudeState = High (deviant value)
        ## Influence of alarm 'ST-V' on process-level (cardiac contraction / depolarization) not made explicit. Interpretation of the alarm solely dependend on a single lead is not clinically feasible.
